!begin_node fnts_get_no_styles

(!begin_liste) [Availability]

!item [Name:]
ØFont selector get number of stylesÆ - Obtain number of styles of a font family.

!item [Opcode:]
184 (sub-opcode 0)

!item [Syntax:]
int16_t fnts_get_no_styles ( FNT_DIALOG *fnt_dialog, int32_t id );

!item [Description:]
The call fnts_get_no_styles obtains the number of styles of a font. The
following apply:

!begin_table [l|l]
Parameter !! Meaning
!hline
(!I)fnt_dialog(!i) !! Pointer to management structure
(!I)id(!i) !! ID of a font of the family
!end_table

(!B)Hint:(!b)
The parameter (!I)id(!i) is the ID of a font of this family, that may have been
returned by fnts_evnt for instance.

!item [(!nolink [Return]) value:]
This function returns the number of styles belonging to the family.

!item [Availability:]
The presence of this call should be checked for using
(!link [appl_getinfo][%apgi_7]) (Opcode 7).

!item [Group:]
Font selection

!item [See also:]
